    "title": "Need and Obligation: avoir besoin de",
    "explanation": "La Ligue a besoin des savants. — the Ligue NEEDS the scientists. The pattern avoir besoin de = to need.\n\nNotice il faut reprendre le travail — il faut + [infinitive] means 'one must.' Both patterns express necessity.\n\nRe-read and find every besoin and il faut. What is needed? What must be done?"
